data.system_settings: MacBook Air Early 2015, MacOS High Sierra 10.13.4, Google Chrome Stable 66.0.3359.181
data.actual_result: Your Username and Discrim ID disappear with the account unclaimed message above.
data.expected_result: Either it goes into user settings without a hitch or it goes to the friends list or most recent channel without problems
data.short_description: Pressing the back button enough times in user settings makes discord load user settings saying your account is unclaimed
data.steps_to_repro: - be already signed in in browser- go to https://discordapp.com/login- click on random servers for a bit- Go to user settings- click the back button until you reach  https://discordapp.com/login again
